[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0735","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0735.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0938","title":"MBone SDR 会话目录工具远程命令执行漏洞","description":"MBone SDR（会话目录）软件包在处理会话启动协议（SIP）消息时，未对用户输入的 shell 元字符进行过滤，导致存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可向运行 SDR 服务的目标主机发送包含恶意 shell 元字符的特制 SIP 消息，从而以服务进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响多个 SDR 软件版本，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0938"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.043","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 MBone SDR Package，该软件自 1999 年后无任何安全更新。建议迁移至现代会话目录工具（如基于 Web 的会议调度系统）替代。若必须继续使用旧版 SDR，应在应用层严格过滤 SIP 消息中的 `;&|`$()` 等 shell 元字符，同时在网络防火墙层面限制仅允许可信来源 IP 访问 SDR 服务端口（UDP 9875），以降低远程利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0938"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0735.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1081","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1365","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统在查找关键系统程序（如 NDDEAGNT.EXE、EXPLORER.EXE、USERINIT.EXE 或 TASKMGR.EXE）时，默认优先搜索 %systemroot% 用户主目录而非系统目录。由于该目录默认可写，本地攻击者可将木马程序放入其中，系统启动或调用时优先执行恶意程序，从而绕过访问限制或提升权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1365"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.093","remediation":"限制 %systemroot% 目录的写入权限，仅允许 Administrators 和 SYSTEM 账户写入；修改系统路径搜索顺序，确保系统目录（%systemroot%\\system32）优先于用户目录被搜索；建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本，该版本已修复此路径搜索顺序问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93069418400856&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93127894731200&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/515","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2336","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1365.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xwwx-gqwv-7rqx/GHSA-xwwx-gqwv-7rqx.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1365.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f9a5326b-c12e-4178-a970-49378c5906df.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/4a6e09a063689f2d97734100478c1eef6f6dc387/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0346","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0346.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0733","title":"VMware 1.0.1 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"VMware 1.0.1 for Linux 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序在处理 HOME 环境变量时未正确进行边界检查，本地攻击者可通过设置超长 HOME 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行或以目标进程权限执行恶意操作。该漏洞危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.2，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0733"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.623","remediation":"建议立即升级至 VMware 2.0 及以上版本（该版本已修复 HOME 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞），或在启动脚本中对 `$HOME` 进行长度校验（限制不超过 256 字节），同时在 `/etc/security/limits.conf` 中为 vmware 用户设置 `ulimit -s 1024` 缩减栈空间以降低利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19371","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0733.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0733","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0733.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0733.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gw48-hr89-vwq9/GHSA-gw48-hr89-vwq9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0733.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0346.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0512","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0512.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0778","title":"Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向 display 或 query 参数提交超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Xi Graphics Accelerated X 4.0.x 及 5.0 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0778"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:02.353","remediation":"Xi Graphics 公司已停止运营，Accelerated-X 产品已停止维护且无安全补丁可用。建议立即迁移至 X.Org 或 Wayland 等现代 X 服务器；如无法迁移，应严格限制本地用户登录权限，移除受影响用户的 display/query 参数传递能力，并应用最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/488","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19370"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0512.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0992","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0992.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1164","title":"Microsoft Outlook 97/98/2000 X-UIDL Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook 97/98/2000 在解析邮件 X-UIDL 标头字段时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标用户发送包含大量相同 X-UIDL 标头的恶意电子邮件，导致 Outlook 客户端在处理邮件时陷入无限循环或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击者仅需构造特制邮件并发送至目标邮箱即可触发，影响 Outlook 97、Outlook 98 及 Outlook 2000 等多个版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1164"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-25","updated":"1999-06-25","remediation":"Microsoft Outlook 97/98/2000 均已终止支持且不再提供安全更新，建议立即升级至 Microsoft Office 2016 或更高版本（包含 Outlook 新版本）。如无法升级，可在邮件服务器端配置 SMTP 过滤规则，拦截或去重包含相同 X-UIDL 头的邮件，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0992.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0384","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0384.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0748","title":"Red Hat net-tools 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Red Hat net-tools 软件包中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向受影响系统发送特制的网络请求触发该漏洞，导致内存破坏和拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 等早期 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至修复版本或应用厂商提供的补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0748"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.483","remediation":"立即升级 Red Hat Linux 系统中的 net-tools 软件包至 RHSA-1999:017-01 公告中指定的修复版本。对于仍在维护的 RHEL 版本，通过 `yum update net-tools` 安装最新版本；对于已停止支持的旧版系统，建议迁移至受支持的 RHEL 发行版或使用 iproute2 套件替代 net-tools 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999017_01.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0384.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1121","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1121.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1470","title":"Eastman Work Management 密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Eastman Work Management 3.21 存在密码明文存储漏洞，该软件将用户密码以明文形式保存在 Windows 注册表的 COMMON 和 LOCATOR 键值中。本地攻击者可通过读取注册表获取明文密码，进而提升权限。该漏洞影响 Eastman Work Management 3.21 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级至修复版本或限制注册表访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1470"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:30.620","remediation":"立即限制对注册表项 COMMON 和 LOCATOR 的访问权限，仅允许 SYSTEM 和管理员组读取，阻止普通用户查询这两项。同时审查所有使用 Eastman Work Management 3.21 的系统，迁移至受支持的最新版本或替代产品，因为该版本以明文存储密码且厂商已停止安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93034788412494&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/485","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2303"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1121.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0331","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0331.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0731","title":"KDE klock 程序会话锁定绕过漏洞","description":"KDE 桌面环境的 klock 屏幕锁定程序存在输入验证缺陷，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制格式错误的输入数据绕过屏幕锁定验证机制，无需输入正确密码即可解锁当前用户会话，获取未授权的系统访问权限。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.x 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。利用条件为攻击者需具备目标系统的本地访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0731"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.367","remediation":"升级至 KDE 1.1.2 及以上版本（1999年8月发布）即可修复该漏洞。该版本在 kscreensaver 的密码验证流程中增加了 timer.stop() 调用，消除了密码输入与对话框销毁之间的竞态条件，防止恶意格式输入绕过锁屏。如无法升级，作为临时缓解措施可禁用 klock 锁屏程序，改用第三方屏幕锁定工具替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/489","https://github.com/KDE/kde1-kdebase/commit/04906bd5de2f220bf100b605dad37b4a1d9a91a6","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0731.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0731","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0731.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0731.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j8vq-qmgj-pjpx/GHSA-j8vq-qmgj-pjpx.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/stats/explore_metadata.ipynb","https://github.com/Chaomeng-Lu/ICVul/blob/3dc55046764ea049e2a57d982699256e65909db9/scripts/cve_filtering.ipynb","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/woc-hack/kjd/blob/19869588676a19dd91ecd601bd03bb001278289b/output.demo1/out1/log.error"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0331.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0723","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 CSRSS 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的客户端服务器运行时子系统（CSRSS）存在工作线程耗尽漏洞，当所有工作线程均处于等待用户输入状态时，远程攻击者可通过发送大量特制请求耗尽系统资源，导致 CSRSS 无法响应新请求，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0723"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.320","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-021 提供的补丁程序，该补丁确保最后一个 CSRSS 工作线程仅处理无需用户输入的请求，从而防止线程耗尽导致的拒绝服务。对于仍运行 Windows NT 4.0 的系统，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），因为 Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年停止支持，不再接收安全更新。如无法升级，可限制交互式登录用户数量，并监控 CSRSS 线程池使用情况作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ233323","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/478","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-021","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7638326ff3f30ccdb52a67547408dd61f5cdc6cc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0723.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0723","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0723.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0723.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3v56-gpqv-vh3w/GHSA-3v56-gpqv-vh3w.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0723.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000675.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a56c6de-e9f5-4fb6-b3d8-cee33c5464ac.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0873","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1019","title":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 5.0 的 SpectroSERVER 组件在安装时设置了不安全的目录权限，导致本地攻击者可将该目录中的特权可执行文件 processd 替换为特洛伊木马。成功利用该漏洞的攻击者可获得 root 或 Administrator 权限，完全控制目标系统。漏洞利用要求攻击者拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1019"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.087","remediation":"立即修改 Spectrum Enterprise Manager 安装目录（默认路径通常为 /opt/Spectrum 或 C:\\Program Files\\Cabletron\\Spectrum）及其子目录的权限，确保仅 root/Administrator 具有写入权限，普通用户仅保留读取与执行权限；使用 chmod 755 或更严格的权限设置。同时校验 processd 可执行文件的完整性（比对 md5/sha256 哈希值），若发现被替换则从原始安装介质恢复。作为长远方案，建议迁移至仍在维护的网络管理平台。服务器层面配置文件完整性监控（如 Tripwire 或 AIDE），对 processd 等关键二进制文件进行实时变更告警。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398513475&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398713491&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/495","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1019","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1019.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0361","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0361.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0742","title":"Debian Mailman 弱认证权限提升漏洞","description":"Debian 发行版中的 mailman 邮件列表管理软件包存在认证机制缺陷漏洞。由于该软件使用了较弱的身份验证方式（如默认密码或弱加密算法），本地普通用户或未经授权的远程攻击者能够绕过认证限制，获取管理员权限，进而控制邮件列表服务、修改配置或访问敏感邮件数据。该漏洞影响早期 Debian GNU/Linux 发行版中默认安装的 mailman 软件包，利用条件较低，攻击者仅需具备网络访问能力即可尝试利用。官方建议升级至修复版本或加强认证配置。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0742"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Debian mailman 软件包至 1.0rc2-5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 Cookie 认证值可预测的安全问题。如无法立即升级，限制对 mailman 管理 Web 页面的网络访问（如通过防火墙仅允许可信 IP 段访问），并监控管理界面的异常请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/480","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0742.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0742","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0742.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0742.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5qff-3w5h-8m56/GHSA-5qff-3w5h-8m56.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0742.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990623.data","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0361.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0729","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0729.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0929","title":"Novell NetWare Novell-HTTP-Server HTTP GET 请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 4.1/4.11 版本中集成的 Novell-HTTP-Server 及 YAWN Web 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送大量 HTTP GET 请求，导致服务器资源耗尽无法响应正常请求，影响系统可用性。该漏洞影响 Novell NetWare 4.1/4.11 及相关组件版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0929"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.967","remediation":"升级 Novell NetWare 至 5.0 及以上版本（该问题已在后续版本修复），或在 Novell-HTTP-Server/YAWN 配置中限制单 IP 最大并发连接数，同时部署防火墙规则限制同一源 IP 的 HTTP 请求速率，防止大量 GET 请求耗尽服务器资源。如产品已停止支持，建议迁移至现代受支持的操作系统和 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0929"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0729.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1009","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0874","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IIS 4.0 在处理包含 .HTR、.IDC 或 .STM 扩展名的文件请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标服务器发送特制的恶意请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0874"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.250","remediation":"升级到 IIS 5.0 或更新版本（如 IIS 6.0/7.0/8.0+），或在 IIS 4.0 中安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-019 对应补丁。作为缓解措施，在 IIS 管理器中删除 .HTR、.IDC、.STM 的 ISAPI 映射（如不需要），并启用 URLScan 工具过滤畸形请求。若系统已无支持，建议迁移至 Windows Server 2003 或更新系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ234905","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-048.shtml","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD06081999.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-019","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A915","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19248"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1009.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1009.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0730","title":"Debian man-db zsoelim 本地符号链接覆盖漏洞","description":"Debian man-db 软件包中的 zsoelim 程序存在符号链接（Symlink）漏洞。本地攻击者可通过构造恶意符号链接，诱导 zsoelim 程序在处理手册页时将其重定向至目标文件，从而覆盖系统上的任意文件，实现权限提升或破坏系统完整性。该漏洞影响 Debian man-db 2.3.10 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0730"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.240","remediation":"升级 man-db 软件包至 2.3.11 及以上版本，该版本中 zsoelim 不再跟随符号链接处理临时文件。建议运行 apt-get update && apt-get install man-db 更新。作为临时缓解，可在系统层面移除 zsoelim 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/lib/man-db/zsoelim。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0730","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19243","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0730.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0730","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0730.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0730.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9cm4-vwcc-jvg8/GHSA-9cm4-vwcc-jvg8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0730.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990612.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0307","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0307.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0713","title":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX dtlogin 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 系统中的 dtlogin 程序存在权限提升漏洞。该程序在处理用户认证时未能正确验证权限，导致本地攻击者可通过向 dtlogin 发送特制请求或利用其不安全的文件权限，获取 root 权限。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 Compaq Tru64 UNIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0713"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-06-11","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持操作系统。如无法迁移，可移除 dtlogin 程序的 setuid root 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtlogin），并限制可登录控制台的用户组，仅允许受信任管理员使用本地控制台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-044.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0307.toml"}]